                <head>The Union in Danger! Mass Meeting of the People of Augusta</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript>
                    <p>THE UNION IS IN DANGER!</p>
                    <p>MASS MEETING</p>
                    <p>OF THE</p>
                    <p>PEOPLE OF AUGUSTA</p>
                    <p>The undersigned unite in recommending that the people of Augusta,
                        irrespective of parties, assemble in MASS MEETING at Staunton, on</p>
                    <p>SATURDAY, NOV. 17th 1860,</p>
                    <p>to consult as to what steps are necessary for the preservation of the Union
                        in the present alarming condition of our Country.</p>
